<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Navigate to a line</b></p><p>You can open a file in the editor at a particular line. Press <span class="shortcut">&shortcut:GotoFile;</span> (<span class="control">Navigate | File</span>), start typing the filename, and then type <span class="code_emphasis">:</span> followed by the line number.</p><p class="image"><img src="images/ij_tips_gotolinenumber.png" alt="Go to specific line" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>